Subject: drm/i915/display: Share code between intel_drrs_flush and
 intel_drrs_invalidate
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 6bd58b70af2f982344789f3f13c8decd42dc10dd
